      "updated": 1777368698163,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Civil-penalty regime activates.\nTier 1 maximum: greater of\nA$52.7M, 3\u00d7 benefit, or 30% of turnover.\nReasonable-steps defence requires\nan evidence trail that exists\n*before* the contravention.",
