      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777368698163,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Mandatory enforcement. Unregistered\nalphanumeric sender IDs display as\n\"Unverified\" to recipients on day one.\nNon-participating telcos cannot send,\ntransit, or terminate sender ID messages.",
