      "locked": false,
      "text": "Reading these as three separate workstreams double-counts engineering capacity.\nCompliance roadmaps that arrive in Q4 2026 collide with AFCA EDR commencement\n(1 January 2027) and the first wave of public ASI reporting obligations.",
